chsᴿ→chᴿ (CHS.CS r)     zero    = CH.CS
chsᴿ→chᴿ (CHS.NEC `r r) zero    = CH.BOX (chsᴿ→chᴿ `r zero)
chsᴿ→chᴿ (CHS.CDIST r)  zero    = CH.CDIST
chsᴿ→chᴿ (CHS.CUP r)    zero    = CH.CUP
