chsᴿ→chᴿ (CHS.CPAIR r)  zero    = CH.CPAIR
chsᴿ→chᴿ (CHS.CFST r)   zero    = CH.CFST
chsᴿ→chᴿ (CHS.CSND r)   zero    = CH.CSND
chsᴿ→chᴿ (CHS.UNIT r)   zero    = CH.UNIT
chsᴿ→chᴿ (CHS.MP i j r) (suc k) = chsᴿ→chᴿ r k
